      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it's practically spotless inside and out. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feel without the heavy price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have, so don't be shy!",
