    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a linear 8,000 RPM power band. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis integrity is unparalleled, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos overhaul to ensure peak VANOS solenoid and cam gear performance. The exterior retains a swirl-free luster over perfectly preserved factory panels, while the undercarriage is devoid of any fluid seepage or oxidation. With refreshed bushings and original dampers maintaining factory-spec compression and rebound, this vehicle offers the razor-sharp turn-in and neutral handling balance definitive of the M-division's peak era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
