      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its initial purchase. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster with zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear on the bolsters, and the original factory scent lingers. Every switch, button, and electronic system functions with precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, open-checkbook service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that defies its age.",
      "price": 48500.0,
